headline: Citi adds Carnival Corp. to focus list, raises cruise sector estimates
summary: Investing.com -- Citi analysts added Carnival (NYSE:CCL) Corp. to their Focus List and raised price targets across the cruise sector in a note Wednesday, citing enduring supply-demand tailwinds that support a long-term pricing advantage.
